=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong>星期五 <span style=\"color: red;\">獅子山之路</span> 7:30 樂富 <br />\n</strong></span><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/9KQxrNJ.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F9KQxrNJ.png&h=c869dffa&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong>星期六 <span style=\"color: red;\">天水圍親子遊行</span> 2:30 天秀公園</strong></span><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/O0LtKzJ.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FO0LtKzJ.jpg&h=85f2aac9&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong>星期日 <span style=\"color: red;\">金鐘民陣遊行</span> 2:30 東角道</strong></span><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2019/09/12/185803_2cefd2fa1345b60607d92f6a90928d20.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2019%2F09%2F12%2F185803_2cefd2fa1345b60607d92f6a90928d20.png&h=a89435a1&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n幫手做文宣同連儂牆<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6b0ce0fc430d4829e6f2b452633df669876cb151","tid":1563702,"uid":213446,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-12T13:58:00.000Z","msg":"6/10"},{"pid":"943f83306710a497b1e96642e63044d9fab9b884","tid":1563702,"uid":213446,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-12T13:58:21.000Z","msg":"7/10"},{"pid":"b096df1637692ce2396d39348cf96d21c1c48e91","tid":1563702,"uid":213446,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-12T13:58:34.000Z","msg":"8/10"},{"pid":"e3e1768040dd31cff0b0a72a6970e6dbf2771adc","tid":1563702,"uid":2